.title.is-3.mt-4.mb-2 Technology

This software is a web application written in
%a(href="https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/" target="_blank") Ruby
with the
%a(href="https://rubyonrails.org" target="_blank") Ruby on Rails
framework at server side,
%a(href="https://bulma.io" target="_blank") Bulma
and
%a(href="https://jquery.com" target="_blank") jQuery
at client side.
%br
Application data is stored in the famous
%em one-file-database
%a(href="https://www.sqlite.org" target="_blank") SQLite
widely used in many applications.
